{"tid":595512,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"仙氣逼人！王祖賢甫學生相獲網民激讚","createTime":"2018-03-16T17:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T03:23:15.000Z","uid":121608,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8da2a613c80301d799d0ef057d6716eeaeb71bad","tid":595512,"uid":121608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"張國榮版的《倩女幽魂》是經典中的經典，而電影中因飾演「聶小倩」一角而備受注目的女星王祖賢，其氣質至今也沒有一個女星可以媲美。她在2004年拍完《美麗上海》後就淡出影壇，並移居溫哥華鑽研佛學，不過她並沒有忘記她的粉絲，間中都會在社交網分享近況。<br />\n<br />\n王祖賢上個月剛過51歲生日，最近更將中學時期打籃球的相片甫上社交網。身穿鮮黃色球衣的她身型高挑露出修長玉腿，白晢的皮膚、鵝蛋面再加上一雙大眼睛，年紀小小已經仙氣逼人！網友大讚她「美到不行」、更封她為「永遠的女神」！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/011233_7c3cac76732fa2d4f938b252e2e81a8b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F011233_7c3cac76732fa2d4f938b252e2e81a8b.png&h=cd891240&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d02a4a47f393a2af1aa58fb8298bb097bfe21dc1","tid":595512,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T17:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac46794554c2b320c2b035e681f2aab01254e5c2","tid":595512,"uid":145117,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T18:36:33.000Z","msg":"睇咗做王祖藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5daf2090b3499ad6b82dfb01cfa5008fedfe1029","tid":595512,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T19:31:36.000Z","msg":"後生嗰陣真係屈機"},{"pid":"906af741d670e051b01db4ef8780f1a211ebf9e8","tid":595512,"uid":123317,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T19:33:47.000Z","msg":"其實佢係咪一直放唔低過去既輝煌"},{"pid":"81dc5d2febef1d3877b1581529854c514ce3a3f6","tid":595512,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T19:36:49.000Z","msg":"小倩果陣真係正到痴線 <br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好 search 